v2.1.1
added check if burnmem.exe is found
changed run of burnmem.exe from the same dir as burnmem_watchdog.exe instead of cwd
v0.2.0
added master binary capable of restarting the utility if it fails (e.g. in case of OOM exception)
v0.1.1
Removed oom adj, cache mode, includeBufferCache, start/stop functionality as unnecessary for standalone usage in Windows.
Added timer
Added --swap boolean parameter and calculation of swap memory as a part of the whole
v0.1.0
Removed cgroups as it does not exist and cannot be compiled for Windows